701368f-a.text:
Johnson Avenue, at Kappock Street, looking northward. Johnson Avenue continces northward around the right side of the house seen in the center of the view; Kappock Street commences at the fence (left), this side of the school building and skirts the house to the left. The school is Public School No. 24. This area is on Spuyten Duyvil Hill...
October 7, 1927
